{"commentv2": 1, "number": 88, "id": 565492, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Thorshadow", "body": "Does anti-magic shield work on this boss", "date": "2009-01-16T17:11:43-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Yes. We have a lock (health stone ftw), and I'm a blood dps.  1st nova, AMS (didn't see my hp drop at all ~I had roughly 2.1k hp)  2nd nova, made sure I have enough runes and hit vampiric blood+death strike+health stone - back to full hp immediately w/o any heals.  3rd nova, used a runic healing pot and death strike to get back to above 50% hp.   He died within few sec after his 3rd nova. Still got the [url=\"http://www.wowhead.com/?achievement=1867\"]Timely Death[/url] achievement anyway.  Practically DKs need no healing from healer (at least blood anyway) but my pally healer throw me a big hea", "creationdate": "2009-01-16T17:11:44-06:00", "id": 382715, "rating": 2, "commentid": 565492, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "309174", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 89, "id": 566018, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "305475", "body": "K, to make everyones life ALOT easier...\r\n\r\nget a hunter or a shaman in your group.\r\n\r\nHunters use aspect of the Wild, idc if it drops my dps by like 150... it helps, and shamans use nature resist totem.\r\n\r\ndo this and you'll be just fine.\r\n\r\noh... and DO NOT MOVE DURING NOVA. messes people up, and gets Loken away so his aura kills, just stand there in one place and DPS race him down. no moving needed at all.", "date": "2009-01-17T02:48:41-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
